# Cargo
# The backend is a deployable application (a Cargo workspace whose `api` crate is a
# binary), so its Cargo.lock is committed for reproducible builds and to let the
# security audit (`.github/workflows/audit.yml`) trigger on lockfile changes.
# **/Cargo.lock

